\v 21 I'm talkingВҰ124660 about dishonourВҰ124645 as if weВҰ124649 were weak, butВҰ124654 (speakingВҰ124660 foolishlyВҰ124659 again), anything that anyoneВҰ124656 else is brave enough to do, then I will also be brave enough \add to match\add*.
\v 22 Are they Hebrews? I am too. Are they Israelis? So am I. Are they descendants of AbrahamВҰ124670? Me also.
\v 23 \x + \xo 11:23: \xt Acts 16:23.\x*Are theyВҰ124675 Messiah's servants? \add Well,\add* I'm aboveВҰ124678 them (speakingВҰ124677 insanelyВҰ124676 now): I've worked harder, been in prisonВҰ124687 more often, \add endured\add* uncountable beatingsВҰ124691, and been close to deathВҰ124695 more often.
