\v 33 butВҰ124826 I was loweredВҰ124831 down from a windowВҰ124828 in the \add city\add* wallВҰ124834 in a basketВҰ124830 andВҰ124835 thus able to escapeВҰ124836 hisВҰ124839 clutch.
\c 12
\s1 What God showed Paul
