\p
\v 1 It's not appropriateВҰ124842 or beneficialВҰ124846 to be boastingВҰ124840, so I'llВҰ124849 come to \add the\add* visionsВҰ124854 and revelationsВҰ124856 from \nd YahwehВҰ124857\nd*.\f + \fr 12:1 \ft See http://bibledifferences.net/2019/04/24/156-boast.\f*
\v 2 Fourteen yearsВҰ124863 ago I observed a manВҰ124859 who was a believer in \nd MessiahВҰ124861\nd* who was pulled \add up\add* to the thirdВҰ124884 heavenВҰ124885. (I didn'tВҰ124868 know whetherВҰ124865 this physically happened or just in the spiritual \add realm\add*.)
