\v 6 because even if I did wantВҰ124936 to boastВҰ124938, I wouldn't be being foolishВҰ124942, because I would be speakingВҰ124945 the truthВҰ124943. But I'llВҰ124941 refrainВҰ124946 in case anyoneВҰ124949 reckons that I'm more than what they can see or hearВҰ124958 about me.
\p
\v 7 SoВҰ124962 to keep my head from getting too big because of those incredible revelationsВҰ124966, I was givenВҰ124971 a вҖҳthornВҰ124973вҖҷ in my bodyВҰ124975вҖ”Satan'sВҰ124977 messengerВҰ124976 to harass me andВҰ124962 keep me from becoming conceited.
