\v 1 This is the third timeВҰ125293 that I'll be comingВҰ125297 there to youВҰ125300 all. вҖҳEvery account mustВҰ125309 be confirmed by at least twoВҰ125304, \add preferably\add* threeВҰ125308, witnessesВҰ125305.вҖҷ\x + \xo 13:1: \xt Deu 17:6; 19:15.\x*
